pubspec.name: googleapis
pubspec.description: Auto-generated client libraries for accessing Google APIs described through the API discovery service.
Placeholder
pubspec.author: Dart Team <misc@dartlang.org>
pubspec.name: googleapis

pubspec.description:
Auto-generated client libraries for accessing the following APIs:
 adexchangebuyer:v1.3 - Accesses your bidding-account information, submits creatives for validation, finds available direct deals, and retrieves performance reports.
 adexchangeseller:v1.1 - Gives Ad Exchange seller users access to their inventory and the ability to generate reports
 admin:directory_v1 - The Admin SDK Directory API lets you view and manage enterprise resources such as users and groups, administrative notifications, security features, and more.
 admin:email_migration_v2 - Email Migration API lets you migrate emails of users to Google backends.
 admin:reports_v1 - Allows the administrators of Google Apps customers to fetch reports about the usage, collaboration, security and risk for their users.
 adsense:v1.4 - Gives AdSense publishers access to their inventory and the ability to generate reports
 adsensehost:v4.1 - Gives AdSense Hosts access to report generation, ad code generation, and publisher management capabilities.
 analytics:v3 - View and manage your Google Analytics data
 androidpublisher:v2 - Lets Android application developers access their Google Play accounts.
 appsactivity:v1 - Provides a historical view of activity.
 appstate:v1 - The Google App State API.
 bigquery:v2 - A data platform for customers to create, manage, share and query data.
 blogger:v3 - API for access to the data within Blogger.
 books:v1 - Lets you search for books and manage your Google Books library.
 calendar:v3 - Lets you manipulate events and other calendar data.
 civicinfo:us_v1 - An API for accessing civic information.
 civicinfo:v1 - An API for accessing civic information.
 compute:v1 - API for the Google Compute Engine service.
 content:v2 - Manage product items, inventory, and Merchant Center accounts for Google Shopping.
 coordinate:v1 - Lets you view and manage jobs in a Coordinate team.
 customsearch:v1 - Lets you search over a website or collection of websites
 dfareporting:v1.3 - Lets you create, run and download reports.
 doubleclickbidmanager:v1 - API for viewing and managing your reports in DoubleClick Bid Manager.
 doubleclicksearch:v2 - Report and modify your advertising data in DoubleClick Search (for example, campaigns, ad groups, keywords, and conversions).
 drive:v2 - The API to interact with Drive.
 freebase:v1 - Find Freebase entities using textual queries and other constraints.
 fusiontables:v1 - API for working with Fusion Tables data.
 games:v1 - The API for Google Play Game Services.
 gamesManagement:v1management - The Management API for Google Play Game Services.
 gmail:v1 - The Gmail REST API.
 groupsmigration:v1 - Groups Migration Api.
 groupssettings:v1 - Lets you manage permission levels and related settings of a group.
 identitytoolkit:v3 - Help the third party sites to implement federated login.
 licensing:v1 - Licensing API to view and manage license for your domain.
 mapsengine:v1 - The Google Maps Engine API allows developers to store and query geospatial vector and raster data.
 mirror:v1 - API for interacting with Glass users via the timeline.
 oauth2:v2 - Lets you access OAuth2 protocol related APIs.
 orkut:v2 - Lets you manage activities, comments and badges in Orkut. More stuff coming in time.
 pagespeedonline:v1 - Lets you analyze the performance of a web page and get tailored suggestions to make that page faster.
 plus:v1 - The Google+ API enables developers to build on top of the Google+ platform.
 plusDomains:v1 - The Google+ API enables developers to build on top of the Google+ platform.
 prediction:v1.6 - Lets you access a cloud hosted machine learning service that makes it easy to build smart apps
 qpxExpress:v1 - Lets you find the least expensive flights between an origin and a destination.
 reseller:v1 - Lets you create and manage your customers and their subscriptions.
 siteVerification:v1 - Lets you programatically verify ownership of websites or domains with Google.
 storage:v1 - Lets you store and retrieve potentially-large, immutable data objects.
 tasks:v1 - Lets you manage your tasks and task lists.
 translate:v2 - Lets you translate text from one language to another
 urlshortener:v1 - Lets you create, inspect, and manage goo.gl short URLs
 webfonts:v1 - The Google Fonts Developer API.
 youtube:v3 - Programmatic access to YouTube features.
 youtubeAnalytics:v1 - Retrieve your YouTube Analytics reports.
